{"tid":2259753,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"反黑警長涉販毒 續還柙12月再訊","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T05:46:51.000Z","uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"990dab78a062e660a4d6803f25e4db5b6afe9fc7","tid":2259753,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"反黑警長涉販毒 續還柙12月再訊<br />\n2020-10-27 11:14<br />\n<br />\n41歲西九龍總區反黑組警長今年5月涉嫌夥同1男1女販毒，當中控方指在警長的背囊及房間內共檢獲24公斤冰毒，涉案3人今在九龍城法院再訊。裁判官將案件押後6星期至12月8日再訊，以待控方諮詢律政司法律意見，3人沒有保釋申請，續須還柙候訊。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告依次為42歲秦景峯、28歲女被告王若男及41歲警署警長許思漢，各被控一項販毒罪。警長許思漢及女被告王若男被控於今年5月7日，在九龍麼地道帝苑酒店及大坑東道南山邨一單位內販運危險藥物；首被告秦景峯則被控於今年5月6日，在九龍麼地道帝苑酒店販運危險藥物。"},{"pid":"33064ad51141c7bd012e1d0dfb2d6ee69e577df9","tid":2259753,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1907445/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E8%B2%A9%E6%AF%92-%E7%BA%8C%E9%82%84%E6%9F%9912%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1907445%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B2%25A9%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259F%259912%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c1ed1fc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1907445%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B2%25A9%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259F%259912%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A&h=0de453ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1907445/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%