753,"uid":299514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a820aa33d6057d90f827c34f88cb4c542dffb253","tid":2259753,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"明明25公斤<br />\n而家變24公斤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿sir都好肚餓下喎<br />\n索左成1公斤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"隔住口罩都知係道友樣，啲冰真係足料AA+"},{"pid":"59d4a56945336998b11ee35a1ffd9e4b5ee8e403","tid":2259753,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"球季又開鑼<br />\n許sir呢一球腳腳七注<br />\n有今生，無來世<br />\n球迷真係大飽眼福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5846983dbcadd15cad8a2027cd440dfc1cc2e56c","tid":2259753,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"處長頒發獎狀<br />\n<br />\n處長曾蔭培最近頒發獎狀予總行政主任蔡仁生，以嘉許蔡仁生由一九九九年九月至二○○三年七月期間擔任編制及文職人員關係科總行政主任，以及籌辦警務處中國文化學會及警務處文職人員會活動，表現出極高度的專業能力、領導才能、忠耿及盡忠職守。<br />\n<br />\n同時，曾蔭培處長亦頒發獎狀予兩組破案有功的調查人員，其中一組人員為女總督察陳玉珍、高級督察羅君東及警長梁耀強。他們於一九九九年九月至二○○○年二月執行任務，打擊一個活躍於荃灣區組織嚴密的販毒集團期間，表現出極高度的領導才能、專業能力及盡忠職守，結果成功解瓦該集團，檢獲四十五公斤四號海洛英混合物、現金三十三萬元、製毒及包裝工具，以及在原訟法庭將兩名毒販定罪，分別判監六年半及十三年四月，因此獲頒發獎狀，以示讚揚。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">另一組人員為高級督察李志堅及警員許思漢。他們於二○○○年十二月至二○○一年十二月執行反三合會行動期間，表現出專業精神及盡忠職守，結果拘捕及檢控四名毒販、十五名三合會活躍份子，以及瓦解荃灣區兩個惡行昭彰的三合會匪黨，因此獲頒發獎狀，以示褒勉。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/757/chi/i01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F757%2Fchi%2Fi01.htm&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=7ceb4cd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/757/chi/i01.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/757/images/i01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F757%2Fimages%2Fi01.jpg&h=05fc520d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/757/images/i01.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F757%2Fimages%2Fi01.jpg&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=2ce8564a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/757/images/i01.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許sir<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbb8f7bb0561fb4ce9c2ad358dfcb75bd8ba4d8","tid":2259753,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"004f8a092d64318dd4027fae6d5d4f9a789ebc00","tid":2259753,"uid":299514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a820aa33d6057d90f827c34f88cb4c542dffb253","tid":2259753,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"明明25公斤<br />\n而家變24公斤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿sir都好肚餓下喎<br />\n索左成1公斤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"隔住口罩都知係道友樣，啲冰真係足料AA+"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/33497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F33497.jpg&h=c171a0fe&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}